    "Title": "Fanout Index",
    "DescriptionLines": [
        "When a document field is an array, the inner array fields can be indexed in what is called a **Fanout Index.**",
        "",
        "An index entry will be generated per item of the array,",
        "resulting in multiple index entries per document.",
        "",
        "Since this can be an expensive operation, a performance hint is issued in the Studio when the fanout ratio is high (number is configurable)."
    ],

